tips.text: House Chai is out of this world! Pretty much everything on the menu is fantastic!
The baked eggs with chorizo is absolutely glorious. Flat white coffee is amazing as well (they roast their beans on site).
Уютное и тихое место, а главное вкусно! Единственный минус - плохой район. Обязательно попробуйте шашлык и закажите хачапури и попросите принести вам тархун. Наслаждайтесь воспоминаниями о родине.
The 'savoury' cocktails on the bar menu are a real delight - we recommend the truffle martini.
Excellent food, but the meze is very tapas-sized, which is completely unlike a true Greek meal! Spent £35 for two for a 5-meze dish. The deli sells hard-to-find Greek delicacies at very good prices.
Mix the sauces. BBQ + Hot. Top class.
